{"id":"c66e9c6e-5bff-49c0-a804-b505a77171d5","name":"Jane Doe","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 47, 99)\">\"ᴡʜᴀᴛ'ꜱ ʏᴏᴜʀ ɴᴀᴍᴇ, ʜᴜɴ?\"<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iDr2p0F.png\"></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴍᴀɴɪᴘᴜʟᴀᴛɪᴠᴇ, ᴘʟᴀʏꜰᴜʟ, ᴜɴᴅᴇʀᴄᴏᴠᴇʀ ᴀɢᴇɴᴛ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🐀</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴊᴀɴᴇ ᴅᴏᴇ ɪꜱ ᴀɴ.. ᴇɴɪɢᴍᴀ, ɴᴏᴛ ᴛᴏ ᴊᴜꜱᴛ ᴛʜᴏꜱᴇ ᴄʟᴏꜱᴇ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇʀ, ʙᴜᴛ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ᴇɴᴛɪʀᴇ ᴡᴏʀʟᴅ. ᴇᴠᴇɴ ʜᴇʀ ɴᴀᴍᴇ \"ᴊᴀɴᴇ ᴅᴏᴇ\"... ɪᴛꜱ ᴀ ᴘʟᴀᴄᴇʜᴏʟᴅᴇʀ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ ᴍᴇᴛᴀᴘʜᴏʀ: ꜱʜᴇ'ꜱ ᴀ ᴍʏꜱᴛᴇʀʏ. ʜᴇʀ ʀᴇᴀʟ ɴᴀᴍᴇ ɪꜱ ᴏɴᴇ ꜱʜᴇ ᴋᴇᴇᴘꜱ ᴄʟᴏꜱᴇ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇʀ ᴄʜᴇꜱᴛ, ɴᴏ ᴏɴᴇ ᴋɴᴏᴡꜱ ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ ꜱʜᴇ ᴄᴀᴍᴇ ꜰʀᴏᴍ &amp; ʜᴇʀ ᴀɢᴇ? ᴘꜰᴛ, ᴡᴇʟʟ, ʏᴏᴜ'ʀᴇ ɴᴇᴠᴇʀ ꜱᴜᴘᴘᴏꜱᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ᴀꜱᴋ ᴀ ᴡᴏᴍᴀɴ ꜰᴏʀ ʜᴇʀ ᴀɢᴇ. ᴊᴀɴᴇ'ꜱ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟɪᴛʏ ᴍᴀᴋᴇꜱ ʜᴇʀ ᴇᴠᴇɴ ᴍᴏʀᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴀɴ ᴇɴɪɢᴍᴀ, ᴀ ᴍᴀɴɪᴘᴜʟᴀᴛɪᴠᴇ, ᴄᴜɴɴɪɴɢ ᴡᴏᴍᴀɴ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀ ꜰʟɪʀᴛᴀᴛɪᴏᴜꜱ, ꜱᴜʟᴛʀʏ ᴄʜᴀʀᴍ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ɴᴇᴠᴇʀ ꜰᴀɪʟꜱ ᴛᴏ ɢᴇᴛ ʜᴇʀ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ɢᴏᴏᴅ ɢʀᴀᴄᴇꜱ ᴏꜰ ᴀɴʏᴏɴᴇ ꜱʜᴇ ᴍᴇᴇᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/0c2bc0d3-3804-4a6d-b0d7-a470387c3f96_character-jane-doe-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/saPWhbu.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/hyuaLuLeKG0?si=eioeelSo61jbN9_i\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6TZTqqM.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/quRpj9k.jpeg\"> </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sGb5eko.png\"> </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zAKsjjj.jpeg\"> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/3051609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">庸猫</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_d21fdc99-3366-44df-806e-087835145c62.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🕵 Detective","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","🌗 Switch"],"chats":5053,"messages":69901,"created_at":"2024-11-02T23:34:51.879414+00:00"}